label: quantitySpecifiedEventElement
comment: A quantity event element specified for this TT object event.
A quantity event element specified for this TT transaction event.

rangeIncludes.comment: Information about an event in which a Track and Trace (TT) element of one of more physical or digital objects is identified by a specific object class identifier (such as an electronic product class), either a specific quantity or an unspecified quantity.

domainIncludes.comment: Information about an event concerning one or more physical or digital Track and Trace (TT) objects identified by instance or class level identifiers.
Information about an event declaring that certain objects have been associated or disassociated with one or more Track and Trace (TT) trade transactions.
